data.description: Welcome to this stunning four bedroom, three bathroom block house in the middle of Clearwater, FL. When you step inside the home you will be greeted by a spacious dining and living area, perfect for entertaining family and friends. The well-designed layout ensures a seamless flow between rooms, creating an atmosphere of ease and relaxation. The kitchen is a true culinary haven, featuring modern appliances, sleek countertops, and ample cabinet space for all your cooking essentials. Whether you're preparing a quick meal or hosting a dinner party, this kitchen is sure to impress. The four bedrooms provide a great location for both privacy and comfort. With generous dimensions, each bedroom offers ample space for relaxation and personalization. The three bathrooms, including an en-suite in the master bedroom, ensure convenience for the entire family. As you step outside, you'll discover a backyard oasis that's perfect for enjoying the Florida sunshine. The highlight of this property is undoubtedly the sparkling pool, inviting you to take a refreshing dip on hot summer days or simply unwind by the water's edge. Located in the sought-after city of Clearwater, this home offers a great location with easy access to a variety of amenities. Whether you're looking to explore the vibrant downtown area, relax on the beautiful beaches, or enjoy the numerous shopping and dining options nearby, this property is ideally situated to fulfill your every need. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a four bedroom, three bathroom block house with a pool and a fantastic location in Clearwater, Florida. Schedule your showing today and envision the wonderful memories waiting to be made in this exceptional home.
